        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 32a178ff-7271-42bb-b266-4447614e229a).Image",
        "Description": "You have, no doubt, made use of the control box as a convenient location to eliminate previous targets from range. But have you ever wondered if it were so easy to do the reverse?\r\rTwo race directors, each on the verge of being investigated for their involvement in bet fixing. Our client wishes to avoid potential loose ends and send a message in a single strike.\r\rI shall leave you to prepare.",
